  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>Yes</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To assess and quantify the changes in bone mineral density between the ARIMIDEX and ARIMIDEX
      plus NOLVADEX groups when compared to the NOLVADEX alone treatment group whilst receiving
      trial therapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
